<plot>Does Custer deserve one last chance? This darkly comic film follows an emotional journey through strange and beautiful landscapes. Scripted by award-winning writer David Greig with precise direction from newcomer Marisa Zanotti, At The End of The Sentence offers us cracking lines, Stephen McCole's great central performance, and a shimmering night-time Glasgow.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?049687</url></doc>
